   </div>
      <hr>
      <h3>INPUT CONVENTIONS</h3>
      <div class="description2"><strong>Punctuation</strong> - Field 581 ends with a period unless another mark of punctuation is present.
      </div>
      <div class="description2"><strong>Display Constant</strong> - Introductory term <em>Publications:</em> is not carried in the MARC record. It may be
                     system generated as a display constant associated with the first indicator value.
         <div class="table">
            <table>
               <tr>
                  <td width="128" align="left" valign="top"><u>First indicator</u></td>
